      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OREGON CALDWELL (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (23.12) from Box 1 at this track. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Racing well and deserves a win. KIA KEEPING (4) has a strong record here with eight wins and five placings from 19 starts. Was out of placings last time (35.62) at The Meadows in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 12 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. WESTERN EMPIRE (5) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 23.29 beating Aston Azul. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from five starts. Can make it back-to-back wins. ASTON DARWIN (2) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
